{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxindeterminate"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situa